# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Second Brain Generator — .gitignore
# Secrets and OS files must NEVER be committed.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Secrets & credentials ──────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*_token
*_secret
credentials.json
secrets.json
.netrc

# ── macOS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes

# ── Editors ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Obsidian ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
vault/.obsidian/

# ── Claude Code — non-portable local files ──────────────────────────
.claude/settings.local.json
# Local instructions auto-loaded by Claude Code (personal override, not committed).
# In THIS repo we use it for the DEV context (an @DEVELOPING.md), which therefore
# must NOT ship with "Use this template".
CLAUDE.local.md

# ── Files generated by installer.mjs (contain an absolute path, ─────────
#    machine-specific → regenerated on each clone, never committed)
.mcp.json
.claude/settings.json
# NB: CLAUDE.md is generated by the installer but does NOT contain an absolute path.
# Deliberately left committable: it's your constitution, it must travel between
# your machines. (In THIS template repo there's only CLAUDE.md.template.)

# ── Node / RAG ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
rag/.cache/
rag/dist/
local-mirror/dist/

# ── Misc ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
.cache/
tmp/
